Privacy Policy
This application owned by Binary and Bricks Private Limited. The company is registered on 16 July 2019. It is an Indian origin company. Binary and Bricks Pvt Ltd is strongly committed in protecting your Privacy. We at Binary and Bricks Pvt Ltd have taken sufficient security majors to protect your company and your personal Information. Please go through the terms and conditions of our Privacy Policy set out herein below:
Application Data:
We at Binary and Bricks Pvt Ltd never directly share your unwanted data to any person in any condition.
Collection of Data:
Application does not collect any data of users.  These data is not related to any personal data of the user.
Data may collect to analytic purposes like, how many times application is downloaded, how many times it is used, who and from where it is downloaded. But it is strictly for analytic purpose only. We does not share this data to any other person.
Use of Personal Data:
However, if the server space provider as matter of backup or other general practices may transfer the server content between any of the countries in which server provider operates or servers are located to enable the use of the information in accordance with this Privacy Policy, You agree to such cross-border transfers of Personal Information and the risk associated with it.
In addition to the disclosures reasonably necessary for the purposes identified above, Website may disclose your Personal Information to the extent that it is required to do so by law, in connection with any legal proceedings or prospective legal proceedings, and in order to establish, exercise or defend its legal rights.
You hereby authorize us to contact you on the basis of information provided by you while communicating/contacting us through any one of the following platforms:
